Wheeljack-X::

Jackie starts ticking points off on his fingers.  "I'd just like you 
to be ready for the following possible side effects: increased power 
drain from supporting a second spark; physical mutation; mental 
instability; and of course, the chance that his spark may be 
incompatible with your shell and bite the dust anyway - if worst comes 
to worst."

He picks up Blackfang.  "Now let's get him to the medical bay.  This 
is too dicey an operation to do out here."  He starts walking toward 
the aforementioned facility.
